  <summary date="2015-07-29T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">CPI-E Act of 2015

 This bill bases cost-of -living increases in benefits under the Civil Service Retirement System, the Federal Employees Retirement System, military retirement and survivor benefit programs, old-age, survivors, or disability insurance benefit program, and specified veterans benefits programs on increases in the Consumer Price Index for the elderly.</summary>
